<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="M" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Mouldy" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Mouldy,</orth> musty, fusty: <cit><quote>you m. rogue,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 2.4.134" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B II, 4, 134</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>your m. chaps,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 2.4.134" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B II, 4, 134</bibl></cit> <cit><quote>m. stewed prunes,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 2.4.134" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B II, 4, 134</bibl></cit> <cit><quote>things that are m. lack use,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 3.2.119" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 119</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>whose wit was m.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 2.1.115" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. II, 1, 115</bibl></cit>.<lb />Name in <bibl n="shak. 2h4 3.2.109" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B III, 2, 109</bibl> etc.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>